a:17:{s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";s:11:"small_descr";s:90:"V-Gel is a herbal gel that is used for the treatment of vaginitis, cervicitis, leucorrhea.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:137:"V-Gel ist ein pflanzliches Gel und wird zur Behandlung von Kolpitis, Gebärmutterhalsentzündung (Zervizitis) und Luokorrhoe angewendet. ";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:108:"V-gel est un gel à base de herbes qui est utilisé pour le traitement de vaginites, cervicite, leucorrhée.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:99:"V-Gel es un gel herbáceo que es utilizado para el tratamiento de vaginitis, cervicitis, leucorrea.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:89:"V-Gel  è un gel di erba che si usa per il trattamento di vaginite, cervicite, leucorrea.";s:10:"full_descr";s:1833:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>V-Gel is useful when the following symptoms are displayed: vaginal candidiasis, vaginal trichomoniasis, non-specific bacterial vaginitis, prevention of post-operative vaginal infections; cervicitis; leukorrhea.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>1 to 2 gm applied deep inside the vagina twice a day through the calibrated applicator for 7 to 14 days.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Use the medicine as directed by your doctor or health care provider.</p><p>If you miss a dose of this medicine and you are using it regularly, take it as soon as possible. Do not take 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>STORAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p><strong>MORE INFO:</strong><br /><br />Active Ingredients:</p><p>Triphala<br /> Satapatri (Rosa damascena Syn. R.centifolia)<br /> Ela (Elettaria cardamomum)<br /> Punarnava (Boerhaavia diffusa)<br /> Shaileyam (Parmelia perlata)<br /> Nirgundi (Vitex negundo)<br /> Haridra (Curcuma longa)</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>There are no known warnings or precautions for V-Gel usage.</p>
<p>Tell your doctor before using V-Gel, if you are allergic to any medicines.</p>
<p>Use your medicine exactly as directed.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>V-Gel is not known to have any side effects if taken as per the prescribed dosage. <br />More Information<br /><br /><br />The study shows that there is a significant alleviation in the symptoms of vaginitis when treated with V-Gel for a period of 7-14 days applied twice daily. Because of the encouraging findings and patient compliance complimented with absence of side effects, we can safely recommend this herbal gel as a treatment of choice in the treatment of vaginitis.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:7:"23.6511";s:9:"pack_name";s:5:"tubes";s:4:"type";s:2:"gm";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:30;a:10:{i:6058;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6058";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"35.835";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6059;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6059";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"29.06617";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6060;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6060";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"26.80989";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6061;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6061";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.68175";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6062;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6062";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.00487";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6063;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6063";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"24.55361";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6064;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6064";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"24.23129";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6065;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6065";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"23.98954";s:4:"name";s:5:"V-gel";}i:6066;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"6066";s:5:"count